parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS modulator can cause the loss of anti-lock braking system (ABS) function, leading to extended stopping distances, increased risk of accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The ABS warning light illuminates
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the vehicle's wheels lock up
and a loud grinding noise is heard when the ABS brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Failure due to Leaking ABS Modulator
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leakage of brake fluid from the ABS modulator can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake fluid leakage from the ABS modulator
extended stopping distances
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
and the vehicle takes longer to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate function of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to take longer to stop, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle takes longer to stop
the wheels lock up
and a loud grinding noise is heard when the ABS brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of both the airbag and brake systems can cause serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy
and the brakes fail to function properly
causing the vehicle to take longer to stop or lose control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Driver's Side Airbag Failure to Deploy
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side airbag to deploy in the event of a collision can result in serious injury or even death to the driver.
symptoms: Airbag does not deploy during collision
driver sustains injuries
vehicle is totaled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag assembly can cause the airbag to fail to deploy in the event of a collision, and can also cause other issues such as the horn to malfunction.
symptoms: Airbag assembly moves around inside the steering wheel
horn operates intermittently
airbag does not deploy during collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of control of the vehicle, and the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a collision can result in serious injury or even death to the driver.
symptoms: Engine roars and surges
vehicle accelerates out of control
airbag fails to deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to a lack of proper restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract
the seat belt stays loose
the seat belt does not lock
the seat belt retractor spring wears through the plastic casing
the seat belt buckle will not lock
the seat belt releases unexpectedly
the seat belt material becomes loose.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn button can cause the horn to malfunction, leading to a safety risk in emergency situations.
symptoms: Horn buttons break easily
horn stops working
horn buttons get stuck
horn switch needs to be replaced frequently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel or cluster can cause electrical fires, toxic fumes, and malfunctioning of essential vehicle systems, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: Instrument panel lights malfunction
headlights come on suddenly
instrument panel catches on fire
toxic fumes are emitted from the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the vehicle can cause accidents, especially when it occurs at high speeds, and can lead to a loss of control.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls intermittently
vehicle cuts off at highway speeds
difficulty diagnosing and fixing the stalling issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Difficulty accessing the horn button in emergency situations can lead to a safety risk, as the driver may not be able to alert other drivers or pedestrians.
symptoms: Difficulty accessing horn buttons in emergency situations.
